# lab/profiles/default.env — explicit "no overrides" profile.
#
# Scenarios already use cooperative defaults built into their own files
# (e.g. SC_FORCE_USER="pfuser", SC_GROUP="LAB\\Domain Users"). This
# profile exists so `--profile default` is a valid no-op and the
# default vs adversarial choice is symmetric in tooling and CI scripts.
#
# Add nothing here. If you find yourself wanting to override a scenario
# default for ALL scenarios, change the scenario default instead.
